ical polarization data, we find that it included\na major thermal component. Its timing provides an accurate estimate for the\nspin of the primary black hole, chi = 0.313 +- 0.01. The present outburst also\nconfirms the established general relativistic properties of the system such as\nthe loss of orbital energy to gravitational radiation at the 2 % accuracy level\nand it opens up the possibility of testing the black hole no-hair theorem with\na 10 % accuracy during the present decade.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2016 09:08:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
