en about 10 and 4 pc from the\njet base and their magnetic field strengths range between 14 and 176 mG, at the\nfrequencies 2.64 to 86.24 GHz. Finally, the gamma-ray active region is located\nat (1.9 +/- 1.1) pc away from the jet base.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2016 11:48:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-11"}
